### Hadith 3:195

*Narrated 'Abdullah bin 'Amr bin Al-'As:*

"Once Allah's Apostle came to me," and then he narrated the whole
narration, i.e. your guest has a right on you, and your wife has a right
on you. I then asked about the fasting of David. The Prophet replied,
"Half of the year," (i.e. he used to fast on every alternate day).

